<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 12:10:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军确认 210 人被哈马斯扣为人质；人道主义援助进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-live/two-released-american-hostages-arrive-in-israel-idf-continues-attacking-hezbollah-targets/0000018b-5011-dc3c-a5df-dcb9baa70000</link><description>开罗和平峰会开始 ■ 拉法过境点开放接受人道主义援助 ■ 哈马斯公布被释放的美国人质的镜头 ■ 黎巴嫩边境交火仍在继续 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯：4,137 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，约 13,000 人受伤 ■ 84 名巴勒斯坦人自战争开始以来西岸的杀戮</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 04:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-live/two-released-american-hostages-arrive-in-israel-idf-continues-attacking-hezbollah-targets/0000018b-5011-dc3c-a5df-dcb9baa70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡加沙失败的秘诀：无所作为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-secret-to-netanyahus-gaza-failure-do-nothing/0000018b-4e41-dbe0-a38b-cff5a0de0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 01:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/the-secret-to-netanyahus-gaza-failure-do-nothing/0000018b-4e41-dbe0-a38b-cff5a0de0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫澄清：拜登并未将延迟的加沙地面入侵与释放人质联系起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/white-house-clarifies-biden-didnt-link-delayed-gaza-ground-invasion-with-hostage-release/0000018b-4f9e-dbe0-a38b-cffe28510000</link><description>此前有报道称，在卡塔尔斡旋下释放两名美国人质后，拜登确认希望以色列推迟对加沙的地面入侵</description><pubDate>Sat, 21 Oct 2023 00:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article/.premium/white-house-clarifies-biden-didnt-link-delayed-gaza-ground-invasion-with-hostage-release/0000018b-4f9e-dbe0-a38b-cffe28510000</guid></item><item><title>放弃人质将摧毁以色列社会的最终纽带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forsaking-the-hostages-will-destroy-the-final-bond-holding-israeli-society-together/0000018b-4e98-d0de-a7ab-efffdb0e0000</link><description>以色列家庭总是同意将孩子送去军队，相信国家会不惜一切代价来保护他们。加沙 200 名人质被遗弃将颠覆这一局面</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 22:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forsaking-the-hostages-will-destroy-the-final-bond-holding-israeli-society-together/0000018b-4e98-d0de-a7ab-efffdb0e0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的以色列人质被困在人道主义援助和地面袭击之间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-in-gaza-are-trapped-between-humanitarian-aid-and-a-ground-assault/0000018b-4d76-dbe0-a38b-cdf66bdb0000</link><description>以停火换取人质意味着哈马斯得到缓刑，但许多以色列人不想听到这个消息。尽管如此，埃及、土耳其、卡塔尔和德国仍在努力达成协议</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 20:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-in-gaza-are-trapped-between-humanitarian-aid-and-a-ground-assault/0000018b-4d76-dbe0-a38b-cdf66bdb0000</guid></item><item><title>在卡塔尔的调解下，两名被哈马斯囚禁的美国人质获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/two-american-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity-with-qatari-mediation/0000018b-4e84-dbe0-a38b-cff444700000</link><description>这两名人质是自哈马斯 10 月 7 日发动致命袭击以来第一批从加沙获释的人质。估计仍有 200 多人被关押在沿海飞地。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 19:44:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/two-american-hostages-released-from-hamas-captivity-with-qatari-mediation/0000018b-4e84-dbe0-a38b-cff444700000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯释放的美国人质：这是他们的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/american-hostages-released-by-hamas-this-is-their-story/0000018b-4e7a-dbe0-a38b-cffeddc80000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特别项目 ■ 朱迪丝·拉南 (Judith Raanan) 和娜塔莉·拉南 (Natalie Raanan)，来自纳哈尔·奥兹 (Nahal Oz) 的塔玛尔·列维坦 (Tamar Levitan) 的女儿和孙女，从美国来访，庆祝她的 85 岁生日。他们13天前被哈马斯绑架。今天他们被释放了</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 19:43:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/american-hostages-released-by-hamas-this-is-their-story/0000018b-4e7a-dbe0-a38b-cffeddc80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡-哈马斯联盟简史</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-brief-history-of-the-netanyahu-hamas-alliance/0000018b-47d9-d242-abef-57ff1be90000</link><description>14年来，内塔尼亚胡的政策是让哈马斯继续掌权； 2023 年 10 月 7 日的大屠杀帮助以色列总理维护自己的统治</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 19:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-brief-history-of-the-netanyahu-hamas-alliance/0000018b-47d9-d242-abef-57ff1be90000</guid></item><item><title>203个空座位：加沙被扣押的以色列人质家属竖起象征性装置</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/203-empty-seats-families-of-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-erect-symbolic-installation/0000018b-4dda-d0de-a7ab-efff67360000</link><description>这些家庭竖起了安息日空桌，这是一个让人质感到不寒而栗的装置，再次绝望地呼喊着帮助他们把亲人带回家。 “请和我们站在一起！”家人大声喊道</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 19:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/203-empty-seats-families-of-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-erect-symbolic-installation/0000018b-4dda-d0de-a7ab-efff67360000</guid></item><item><title>少数以色列军官从哈马斯恐怖分子手中救出了 90 名新兵。他们付出了生命的代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-few-idf-officers-saved-90-trainees-from-hamas-terrorists-they-paid-with-their-lives/0000018b-4da2-dc3c-a5df-ddaadf370000</link><description>为了阻止哈马斯接管齐金姆训练基地，六名军官和一名新兵在几乎独自发动的战斗中被杀。当战斗的细节开始浮出水面时，恐怖的规模——以及英雄主义的规模——变得清晰起来</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 18:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-few-idf-officers-saved-90-trainees-from-hamas-terrorists-they-paid-with-their-lives/0000018b-4da2-dc3c-a5df-ddaadf370000</guid></item><item><title>近年来，以色列国防军从加沙边境社区夺走了武器，并武装了数千名约旦河西岸定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/idf-took-away-weapons-from-gaza-border-towns-and-armed-w-bank-settlers-in-the-thousands/0000018b-4d6d-dbe0-a38b-cdfd0d4f0000</link><description>以色列军方认为，边境围栏竖起后，恐怖分子入侵的可能性“接近于零”。他们从该地区撤军，将当地安全作为最后一道防线。一位当地安全协调员表示，“尽管我们不断敲桌子，但没有任何帮助。”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 16:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/idf-took-away-weapons-from-gaza-border-towns-and-armed-w-bank-settlers-in-the-thousands/0000018b-4d6d-dbe0-a38b-cdfd0d4f0000</guid></item><item><title>尼尔奥兹不是一场战斗，而是一场系统性的屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-wasnt-a-battle-it-was-a-systematic-massacre/0000018b-4cff-dc3c-a5df-dcff56030000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，以色列国防军首次允许记者进入以色列加沙边境的尼尔奥兹基布兹。这些是《国土报》摄影师 Moti Milrod 拍摄的照片</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 13:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-wasnt-a-battle-it-was-a-systematic-massacre/0000018b-4cff-dc3c-a5df-dcff56030000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡任命处理加沙以色列人质事件的人谴责欧洲特使支持奥斯陆协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/pms-appointee-on-hostages-yells-at-european-envoys-for-supporting-oslo-accords/0000018b-4c75-d5d2-afef-ccfdbcc80000</link><description>在一次讨论释放加沙人质的会议上，ret。双桅船。加尔·赫希 (Gal Hirsch) 将军对欧洲大使 30 年前针对以色列和巴勒斯坦人的政策大喊大叫。一位大使：“我们想提供帮助，不需要政治说教”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 12:22:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/pms-appointee-on-hostages-yells-at-european-envoys-for-supporting-oslo-accords/0000018b-4c75-d5d2-afef-ccfdbcc80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡将面临的耻辱将远远大于他试图逃避的耻辱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/the-shame-that-will-follow-netanyahu-will-be-far-greater-than-one-he-attempted-to-escape/0000018b-4bc8-d1fd-a59f-efdb683d0000</link><description>比比作为“以色列保护者”的神话已经打破。 “一切都结束了，”执政联盟的一名高级成员本周表示。 “政府将无法幸存”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 07:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/the-shame-that-will-follow-netanyahu-will-be-far-greater-than-one-he-attempted-to-escape/0000018b-4bc8-d1fd-a59f-efdb683d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯释放的第一批人质美国母女抵达以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-live/american-mother-and-daughter-first-hostages-released-by-hamas-arrive-in-israel/0000018b-4b06-d1fd-a59f-ef9ff9ed0000</link><description>哈马斯释放了两名美国人质 ■ 随着紧张局势升级，以色列制定了针对黎巴嫩北部边境附近居民的疏散计划 ■ 以色列国防军表示，一夜之间袭击了加沙的 100 多个目标 ■ 拜登要求国会向以色列提供 140 亿美元的军事援助 ■ 至少 1,300 人自 10 月 7 日以来以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯：3,200 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，约 11,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 05:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-live/american-mother-and-daughter-first-hostages-released-by-hamas-arrive-in-israel/0000018b-4b06-d1fd-a59f-ef9ff9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>导致哈马斯袭击的失败永远改变了以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/underprepared-and-overconfident-israel-failed-to-spot-the-signs-of-impending-disaster/0000018b-4976-d03a-afcb-697edb020000</link><description>安全机构热衷于敌人被威慑的观念 ■ 内塔尼亚胡扶植哈马斯，而以色列人却视而不见 ■ 多年来忽视巴以冲突的后果，突然付出了沉重的代价</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 03:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/underprepared-and-overconfident-israel-failed-to-spot-the-signs-of-impending-disaster/0000018b-4976-d03a-afcb-697edb020000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡仍然相信他能够逃避指责并在以色列最大的灾难中幸存下来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-still-believes-he-can-dodge-blame-and-survive-israels-greatest-catastrophe/0000018b-496e-dc3c-a5df-ddeec2aa0000</link><description>加沙边境灾难发生两周后，总理甚至没有暗示要承担责任——与许多高级国防官员不同。与此同时，拜登动员到以色列一边可能会让他以后的事情变得复杂</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 03:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-still-believes-he-can-dodge-blame-and-survive-israels-greatest-catastrophe/0000018b-496e-dc3c-a5df-ddeec2aa0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登将向国会请求 140 亿美元的以色列军事援助：“敌对行为者将知道以色列比以往任何时候都更强大”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-ask-congress-for-unprecedented-14b-in-military-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4a84-d199-a7eb-dfde51e20000</link><description>在罕见的椭圆形办公室讲话中，美国总统将哈马斯与普京进行了比较，称“他们都想彻底消灭邻国的民主国家”</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 00:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-to-ask-congress-for-unprecedented-14b-in-military-aid-for-israel/0000018b-4a84-d199-a7eb-dfde51e20000</guid></item><item><title>“俄罗斯轮盘赌”：以色列遭受轰炸最严重的城市的居民得不到保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</link><description>阿什凯隆是加沙战争中目标最严重的城市，该城的约 40,000 名居民缺乏适当的保护以免受火箭弹袭击——尽管事实上已经为此编列了资金预算</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 22:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/russian-roulette-residents-of-israels-most-heavily-bombarded-city-are-left-unprotected/0000018b-49da-d03a-afcb-69fa722d0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们在达兰萨拉冥想。突然，来自以色列的电话开始涌入”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：在战争期间，一名年轻女子返回以色列的家，而另一名年轻女子则在拉脱维亚与家人团聚</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-10-20/ty-article/.highlight/we-were-meditating-in-dharamshala-suddenly-phone-calls-from-israel-started-pouring-in/0000018b-49bc-d1fd-a59f-edbf900b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>